==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Misbecome
<hw>Mis`be*come"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>Not to become;
to suit ill; not to befit or be adapted to.</def>
<rj><au>Macaulay.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Thy father will not act what <qex>misbecomes</qex> him.</q>
<rj><qau>Addison.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Misbecoming</ent>⟦br⟧
